===============================
=  README for ex9: Asteroids  =
===============================

Simple asteroids game implementation using the turtle module to draw the game graphics.

============
=  Usage:  =
============

python3 asteroids_main.py <asteroids_amount>

==================
=  Description:  =
==================

Simple asteroids game where the player controls a ship in a field of asteroids. The main object of the game is to shoot
the asteroids while trying to avoid collisions with them. When a torpedo hits one of the asteroids it splits it into
smaller ones.

=============================
=  List of submitted files: =
=============================

README		        This file
AUTHORS             Contains list of people who worked on the exercise
asteroid.py         Contains the Asteroid object class implementation
asteroids_main.py   Contains the main game logic
ship.py             Contains the Ship object class implementation
torpedo.py          Contains the Torpedo object class implementation

